column1: From: Smith-Martin et al. (2019) Effects of dry-season irrigation on leaf physiology and biomass allocation in tropical lianas and trees. Ecology 100:e02827
These data are summaries of data available online with the article:
mean_MPa is pre-dawn leaf water potential; it is the mean from replicate trees in replicate plots which were not watered.
Photo.umolCO2 is CO2 flux into a leaf; it is a  measure of photosynthetic rate
